snippet.title: Amber Heard Replaced in Aquaman 2 with Emila Clarke!? - Reality or Rumor?!
snippet.description:
Lots of news is reporting that Amber Heard is being replaced by Jason Momoa's Game of Thrones co-star Emila Clarke in James Wan's Aquaman 2. But what's true about this story? Is Warner Brothers replacing Amber Heard? Has she already been fired from Aquaman 2? Is there a Mera TV series coming to HBO Max starring Amber Turd? We'll discuss it all.
